Coloration of holotype in life: Dorsum reddish tan with dark brown markings, including labial bars, interocular bar, diagonal bars on flanks, transverse bars on limbs, and with broad cream band across top of head and upper eyelids (
Fig. 2
); venter dull pale orange with brown flecks and reticulations; iris reddish tan dorsally, grayish bronze below narrow median black triangular marks.
